| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2841 — Recovery Inhibition (babuk2)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f139c9cd-965c-5aa8-9f4a-8ff2d8d32a7f"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
